{"tid":1817413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷買無良公司雪花秀 垃圾公司唔俾帶口罩","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T09:55:24.000Z","uid":185991,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ff76cd11c9ffcf525dac71eb55c26aa98ed25262","tid":1817413,"uid":185991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司雪花秀<br />\n漠視員工生命安危<br />\n之前每逢有光復行動，警暴時都長期唔比員工早收工<br />\n等到放晒催淚彈 成個商場都係防暴狗嘅時候<br />\n先至推啲員工去死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次中国肺炎死人<br />\n傳染率咁高<br />\n都唔肯比員工戴口罩防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n零售前線每日接觸咁多人 仲有咁多大陸人去買護膚品<br />\n政府唔做嘢，你仲要剝削埋員工保護自己嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死撚咗係咪你賠返條命俾我啊？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n帶口罩就一定要有醫生紙<br />\n如果唔係 就調你去無人嘅鋪頭<br />\n即係攞你份人工大你啦 咁同禁聲有咩分別啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗無良 我諗唔到有咩可以形容呢啲垃圾公司<br />\n各位絲打千祈唔好再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買護膚品我唔好幫襯袁彌明？大把黃店選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我再一次話俾你哋班冇腦戇鳩知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家我戴口罩唔係我有問題<br />\n係你唔戴口罩你好撚有問題啊！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n冇客入嚟間鋪頭你啲員工咪唔使戴口罩囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝雪花秀集團生意蒸蒸日上<br />\n做下一間海港城Gucci<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/09/132005_5df93fc2b4d94bb77fd02c2dc2eb6773.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F09%2F132005_5df93fc2b4d94bb77fd02c2dc2eb6773.png&h=1c649b76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"619690801d4498d716d0e402505ae594794000ea","tid":1817413,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"11b6ad08ae57f60d8f78ef7914dd93a666371ae6","tid":1817413,"uid":185991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司雪花秀<br />\n漠視員工生命安危"},{"pid":"4b13fdf0ce47e04beb090f0a51f2aed8522065ed","tid":1817413,"uid":251265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"雪花秀係好多中國國企合作<br />\nBtw 垃圾牌子 無宋慧喬既話根本無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d40e8db37da8ddc4c8b4f8e0e2cc0d5e95db76a","tid":1817413,"uid":185991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b13fdf0ce47e04beb090f0a51f2aed8522065ed","tid":1817413,"uid":251265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"雪花秀係好多中國國企合作<br />\nBtw 垃圾牌子 無宋慧喬既話根本無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"一齊罷買 <br />\n垃圾公司留返比垃圾小粉紅買"},{"pid":"40932e50540f07338a3e90c956de1ecb1d74e24e","tid":1817413,"uid":185991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司雪花秀<br />\n漠視員工生命安危"},{"pid":"32e77cf9e39b7eb1a1886a024d2a992eb1f8cb24","tid":1817413,"uid":185991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"奶共垃圾公司雪花秀<br />\n漠視員工生命安危<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxVF